msContents.summary: 280 letters, including some autograph letters of Panciatichi, secretary of state for the Grand Duchy of Tuscany, to Anton Francesco Montauti, special envoy from Tuscany to the imperial court in Vienna.

msItem.title: Lettere di segretario di stato scritte al Marchese Montauti inviato di Tuscana alla corte cesarea
msItem.author: Panciatichi, Francesco
Montauti, Anton Francesco, Abbe Marquis

supportDesc.extent: 548 leaves : 288 x 204 mm. bound to 310 x 224 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 548; [1-548]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in various cursive scripts by several scribal hands, with some autograph letters.

origin.p: Written mostly in Florence, some in Pisa, 1691-1699.
